data.description: Welcome Home! See all that Roxborough has to offer!  With Main floor Primary, this charming three-bedroom, two bath home is waiting for you.  With its warm and inviting ambiance, this residence offers a perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Step into a generously sized living room and family room that welcome you with plenty of natural light and New windows. This space is perfect for family gatherings or relaxing by the fireplace. The eat-in kitchen features ample counter and storage space, with wine fridge included. The upstairs offers 2 bedrooms and a full shared bath. The low maintenance front yard and backyard are perfect for summer BBQ's or relaxing evenings. If that was not enough, this home has an FHA assumable loan. Enjoy the beautiful Colorado weather from the comfort of your own home. Roxborough offers a fantastic community with Hiking, walking, running, fishing, boating, biking, golfing, and more…  There are also several community events like: summer concerts, Trunk-or-Treat, food trucks, movies, egg hunts, breakfast with Santa, networking, and more.
